ROASTED LAMB SHANKS

Lamb shanks in baking dish
Add rosemary, garlic, and potatoes
Season with oil, salt pepper
Cover with foil
Bake at 350 for 45min
Remove foil and bake at 400 for 15min

Serve


STOCK

Oil in Dutch Oven
Add Onion, carrot, celery, garlic
Saut√© until browned
Add bay leaf, peppercorns
Toast for 2min
Add white wine (beer?) and deglaze
Reduce by half
Add bones
Add 2L water
Bring to a boil
Skim
Add parsley and thyme
Simmer for 4hrs
Remove to cool, then refrigerate



STOBHACH

Butter in dutch oven
Brown lamb
remove
Brown leeks and carrots
Add meat, potatoes, and stock
Cover and bake for 1-2hrs

Serve sprinkled with parsley

